description: This file serves as the entry point for a React-based web application. It imports necessary modules such as React, ReactDOM, CSS styles, and the main App component. It initializes the React rendering process by attaching the App component into the DOM element with id 'root'.

methods.name: ReactDOM.createRoot
methods.description: Creates a root for rendering React elements into the DOM.

methods.name: root.render
methods.description: Renders JSX elements into the React root element.
